{"tid":379986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝導彈飛越上空　日企要職員「如常返工」","createTime":"2017-08-29T18:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T00:53:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7641c2591726c32ff584a51248cb3021c2e75bb6","tid":379986,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:46:02.000Z","msg":"北韓周二（29日）再次發射導彈挑釁，今次更飛越日本的北海道，引發日本方面的恐慌。此時有日本企業向員工發送電郵，不過並非關心下屬安全，而是要他們如常返工。 <br />\n<br />\n有日本網民在Twitter上表示，在北韓導彈於早上飛過日本後，自己收到上司的電郵，內容令自己大笑起來，當中寫道：「北韓的導彈似乎已飛過日本上空，請如常返工。」貼文迅速瘋傳，吸引多達92萬人分別轉發及讚好，更有不少網民留言。 <br />\n<br />\n有人指這封電郵的破壞力不比導彈少，有人亦批評該上司缺乏危機意識。有網民戲言，等導彈落入日本再休息便遲了，甚至稱：「就算世界毀滅都要上班！」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門正式同日本接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/mobile/bknint-20170829183844188-0829_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170829%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170829183844188-0829_17011_001.html&d=pjaYt0RjaqmNpsRvj%2FdAAZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=9de45a2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/mobile/bknint-20170829183844188-0829_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9cef42e9fe873e8fabc16e3d170508b4cf5a0d17","tid":379986,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:25:23.000Z","msg":"香港咪一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬寧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0cef5a78d8c3f6e6e315367b2b3a1fda2a3cc2","tid":379986,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"有幾閒"},{"pid":"35819f5ec8a9608a9d9c4ae421b7cb847e1b08dc","tid":379986,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65842da31b368dddee09d950a63b234e5caca0f4","tid":379986,"uid":